=======================
 Environmental Geology
=======================

:status: hidden


Environmental Geology (ERS 102) covers how humans impact and are impacted by geologic processes. This includes geologic hazards (e.g. earthquakes), environmental polution (e.g. groundwater contamination), and climate change. I plan to enhance this page to include information on these topics. A `syllabus <{static}../../images/ERS102_syllabus.pdf>`_ may be reviewed that outlines the structure of this class and topics covered.

